            "answer_text": "Security. It is now often overlooked, but prior to the 19th century, Germany was basically, along with Italy, Europe\u2019s stomping ground. Do you have a war you want to fight? There are lovely places in Germany or Italy to do it. And you might even find some nice local auxiliaries. Burn, loot, rape and pillage to your hearts content the locals won\u2019t be able to stop you. Only once the Italians and the Germans unified were they able to secure peace for their countries. ",
